{
  "texts": [
    "Variant-1 and Variant 2 relatively disfavor the Leibniz Association, whereas Variant-0 disfavors the Helmholtz Association, when comparing all five variants.",
    "The same holds for the universities, which reach lower shares of HCRs at Variant-0.",
    "Next to Variant-0, Variant-1 is most unfavorable for the Fraunhofer Society.",
    "For the universities of applied sciences, Variant-1 and Variant-4 are unfavorable.",
    "The various analyses of the HCRs on the organizational level show that the institutional characteristics of the HCRs lists are different -if we take a closer look at German institutions."
  ]
}